Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so today we will discuss the Bronze Age collapse.\N{\rChinese}好的，今天我们要讨论古代黄土壳的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:07.06,English,,0,0,0,,I want to paint you a picture\N{\rChinese}我想给你们画一幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:10.96,English,,0,0,0,,of the world in about 1200 BCE.\N{\rChinese}大约1200年后回到古代黄土壳的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.54,English,,0,0,0,,So, in this world,\N{\rChinese}好的，先在这片大地里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.14,English,,0,0,0,,the center of this world\N{\rChinese}好的，先在这片大地里，先后??
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:21.54,English,,0,0,0,,is what we call Mycenaean Greece.\N{\rChinese}好的，先后????
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:28.04,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, across from the Mycenaean Greece,\N{\rChinese}好的，跨越古希腓里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:31.52,English,,0,0,0,,across the Aegean Sea, okay, this is the Aegean,\N{\rChinese}好的...??…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:35.82,English,,0,0,0,,is what we call Anatolia.\N{\rChinese}??…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:40.48,English,,0,0,0,,Today we refer to Anatolia as Turkey, okay?\N{\rChinese}今天我们把安塔尔尼亚称作土耳古里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:42.54,English,,0,0,0,,And in Anatolia,\N{\rChinese}And in Anatolia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:43.94,English,,0,0,0,,the Hittite Empire\N{\rChinese}...
