Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.52,English,,0,0,0,,Further south is a place called Cyprus.\N{\rChinese}进一步南方有一个叫做柯普利亚的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:54.06,English,,0,0,0,,Canine, okay? Canine is important\N{\rChinese}Canine...??…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:57.10,English,,0,0,0,,when we do the Bible\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.56,English,,0,0,0,,because that is the birthplace of the Israelites.\N{\rChinese}??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:04.80,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, so Canine today is what we refer to as Lebanon,\N{\rChinese}好的，...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.62,English,,0,0,0,,Syria,\N{\rChinese}翻译：
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:08.46,English,,0,0,0,,and Israel today.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.38,English,,0,0,0,,Canine is a province of the Egyptian Empire, okay?\N{\rChinese}Canine...??…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:17.26,English,,0,0,0,,So this is Egypt, okay?\N{\rChinese}??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:20.76,English,,0,0,0,,Over here,\N{\rChinese}在此处，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:24.16,English,,0,0,0,,is a place called Mesopotamia.\N{\rChinese}在此处，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:28.66,English,,0,0,0,,And we today call Mesopotamia Iraq.\N{\rChinese}在此处，伊斯兰语为伊拉克。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:34.64,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Over here is today what we call Iran.\N{\rChinese}在此处，伊斯兰语为伊拉克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.88,English,,0,0,0,,Back then it was basically Persia.\N{\rChinese}回到那时，基本是波斯。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.60,English,,0,0,0,,Over here is Afghanistan.\N{\rChinese}在此处是阿富尼亚。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:42.84,English,,0,0,0,,And then next to Afghanistan is India.\N{\rChinese}接着在阿富尼亚旁边是印度。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.78,English,,0,0,0,,And of course, remember these are the steps.\N{\rChinese}接着在阿富尼亚旁边是印度。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:54.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? So for Mesopotamia and Greece, you also had the Mediterranean.\N{\rChinese}好的？所以在美索波提亚和希腊里，你们也有地中海。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:59.32,English,,0,0,0,,And over here are the islands of Cyprus and Crete.\N{\rChinese}在此处是塞浦里亚和克里特岛。”]\}We need to translate cues [31] and [32] into Simplified Chinese. Provide JSON array translations. Ensure each translation string may contain at most one newline. Use natural Chinese. Let's translate: cue 31:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:05.26,English,,0,0,0,,And then over here is a place called Iberia.\N{\rChinese}在此处是伊比利亚。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.50,English,,0,0,0,,And over here is Britain.\N{\rChinese}在此处是英国。
