Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:24.72,English,,0,0,0,,And what's really important for you to recognize about this world is it's interconnected.\N{\rChinese}在此处是伊比利亚。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:30.08,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that they are trading and communicating with each other.\N{\rChinese}在此地是英国。”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.58,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? This is what we call the Bronze Age.\N{\rChinese}好的？这就是我们所说的青铜时代。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.60,English,,0,0,0,,The Bronze Age.\N{\rChinese}青铜时代。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.36,English,,0,0,0,,And why is it called the Bronze Age?\N{\rChinese}为什么叫青铜时代？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:41.12,English,,0,0,0,,Because they're trading basically bronze during this period.\N{\rChinese}因为在此期间他们基本上在交易青铜。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:45.56,English,,0,0,0,,Back then, bronze is like oil today.\N{\rChinese}回到那时，青铜就像今天的石油。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? It is the basis for the economy.\N{\rChinese}好的？它是经济的基础。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:52.08,English,,0,0,0,,The very structure of their economy.\N{\rChinese}铜的结构就是其经济结构。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:57.24,English,,0,0,0,,Bronze is an alloy made of copper\N{\rChinese}铜合金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.22,English,,0,0,0,,and tin.\N{\rChinese}和锡。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:03.18,English,,0,0,0,,Copper and tin you have to mine.\N{\rChinese}铜与锡你需要开采。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.44,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And only a few places will have these resources.\N{\rChinese}OK? 只要几处…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:10.64,English,,0,0,0,,So tin is found in Britain,\N{\rChinese}在英国、伊比利亚、安塔利亚发现的锡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:15.04,English,,0,0,0,,in Iberia, in Anatolia,\N{\rChinese}在英国、伊比利源里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.40,English,,0,0,0,,in Afghanistan. Okay?\N{\rChinese}in Afghanistan.Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:22.10,English,,0,0,0,,Copper is mainly found in Cyprus\N{\rChinese}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.12,English,,0,0,0,,and Crete and\N{\rChinese}和克里特岛以及在安塔利亚里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.64,English,,0,0,0,,also in Anatolia.\N{\rChinese}在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? Now, meaning\N{\rChinese}OK? 现在…
