Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.54,English,,0,0,0,,From India to Britain.\N{\rChinese}From ... ... ... …
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:52.48,English,,0,0,0,,Even China over here was part of this world\N{\rChinese}翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.88,English,,0,0,0,,but not to the degree as these other places.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.90,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? In this world,\N{\rChinese}OK? 在此...??
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:04.40,English,,0,0,0,,there are different ways that you can profit or make money.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.76,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? The first way is mining.\N{\rChinese}OK? 先后??
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:13.36,English,,0,0,0,,So basically extracting resources, tin and copper in order to make bronze.\N{\rChinese}...
