Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.32,English,,0,0,0,,Basically profit the most from trading.\N{\rChinese}基本上是那种最能赚取利润的商人。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.54,English,,0,0,0,,If you look at this map, who would make the most money from trading?\N{\rChinese}...
