Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:07.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And this place over here,\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.60,English,,0,0,0,,you look at the map, it becomes the center of the world\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.64,English,,0,0,0,,because this place.\N{\rChinese}因为这地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:17.32,English,,0,0,0,,This place becomes the logistics hub of the world.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.40,English,,0,0,0,,To get to anywhere, you have to pass through this place.\N{\rChinese}到达任何地方都要经过此处。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:24.70,English,,0,0,0,,And so this place can basically collect tolls.\N{\rChinese}到达此处后再往后面
