Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.36,English,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know? Yeah,\N{\rChinese}??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.78,English,,0,0,0,,it's the toll gate of the world.\N{\rChinese}它是世界的关口。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:37.46,English,,0,0,0,,Right? You have to pass through this place in order to access other places.\N{\rChinese}对了，先到此处才能到达其他地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.58,English,,0,0,0,,Therefore, this place is very wealthy.\N{\rChinese}...
