Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.06,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, we will do the Iliad next semester.\N{\rChinese}好的，下一学期我们会做《伊利亚特》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.66,English,,0,0,0,,We will discuss the Iliad in the next class.\N{\rChinese}我们在下一节课里讨论《伊利亚点》
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.60,English,,0,0,0,,But I want you to understand this place is called Troy.\N{\rChinese}但我想让你们知道这地方叫做特洛伊。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.34,English,,0,0,0,,And because this place is so important, for centuries,\N{\rChinese}因为它是个很重要的地方，长久以来一直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.86,English,,0,0,0,,they've been fighting wars over this place.\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:13.50,English,,0,0,0,,Because it's really the center of the universe.\N{\rChinese}因为它是宇宙的中心。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:18.40,English,,0,0,0,,Right? If you can control this place, you become very wealthy because everyone has passed through you.\N{\rChinese}对吧？如果能在此处掌握一手，便可把握手掌握。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.98,English,,0,0,0,,You can collect tolls.\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.80,English,,0,0,0,,You can trade. Okay?\N{\rChinese}你可以做交易。好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:27.14,English,,0,0,0,,Does that make sense? And the last way you can make money off this world is what?\N{\rChinese}它们好像？…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.90,English,,0,0,0,,What's the last way in which you can make a lot of money in this world?\N{\rChinese}…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.68,English,,0,0,0,,You can do it through mining, industry, trading.\N{\rChinese}你可以通过矿业、工业、贸易来做事。
