Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.42,English,,0,0,0,,Piracy. Right?\N{\rChinese}Piracy. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:57.56,English,,0,0,0,,So, when we read the Iliad, what you will discover is the Greeks\N{\rChinese}...
