Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.60,English,,0,0,0,,It was a globalized world.\N{\rChinese}它是一个全球化的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.92,English,,0,0,0,,We call this globalization. But at the same time,\N{\rChinese}我们把它称为全球化。但与此同时，
